data.description: Professional Photos are coming soon.    Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom split foyer entry townhouse nestled in the desirable neighborhood of Benjamin's Claim. This home offers a unique and welcoming design with three well-defined levels. Upon entering this well maintained home, you'll be greeted by the updated wood plank flooring that flows seamlessly through the main and upper levels, creating a warm and modern ambiance. The spacious eat-in kitchen is a focal point, boasting not only functionality but also a pass-through dining area, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying family meals. The upper floor hosts three bedrooms, providing comfortable living spaces, and continuing the stylish wood plank flooring for a cohesive look. The lower level features wall-to-wall carpeting, creating a cozy retreat for relaxation or casual gatherings. The finished lower level adds versatility to the home, serving as an ideal space for a family room, home office, or even a guest suite.  The large shed has electric run to it so you can turn it into a workshop.   The townhouse is situated in a tranquil cul-de-sac, providing a peaceful and safe environment.  Conveniently located in close proximity to Frederick, MD, Washington, DC, and Baltimore, MD, this townhouse offers easy access to major routes such as RT 32, Rt 26, and Rt 70, making commuting a breeze. The neighborhood is well-connected, close to schools, shopping centers, and various amenities, ensuring that all your daily needs are within reach. With its modern updates, practical layout, and strategic location, this split foyer entry townhouse in Benjamin's Claim is the epitome of comfortable and convenient living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful property your new home!
